<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 03:11:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国计划制定市场准入新规则：李总理向全球首席执行官致辞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-new-rules-market-access-data-flows-premier-li-tells-global-ceos-2024-03-24/</link><description>中国总理李强周日对全球首席执行官和中国政策制定者表示，中国将仔细研究市场准入和跨境数据流动问题，并将很快在这些领域颁布新的法规。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 02:51:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-new-rules-market-access-data-flows-premier-li-tells-global-ceos-2024-03-24/</guid></item><item><title>太阳重返迈阿密，斯瓦泰克追逐“阳光双打”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/pegula-advances-after-zhu-retires-play-resumes-miami-open-2024-03-23/</link><description>经过两天的降雨后，周六迈阿密公开赛迎来了阳光，这对伊加·斯瓦泰克来说是个好兆头，她以 6-1 6-6 的轻快比分，发起了挑战，成为第二位不止一次赢得“阳光双打”的女性选手。 1胜意大利选手卡米拉·乔治。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 20:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/pegula-advances-after-zhu-retires-play-resumes-miami-open-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁“纠正错误”赋予中远集团在大型港口的独家经营权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/peru-correct-error-that-gave-cosco-exclusivity-megaport-2024-03-23/</link><description>秘鲁港务局表示，希望纠正一个“行政错误”，该错误导致中国中远海运集团获得了新钱凯大型港口的独家经营权。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 14:23:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/peru-correct-error-that-gave-cosco-exclusivity-megaport-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度活动人士绝食争取拉达克自治吸引了数千名支持者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-activists-hunger-strike-ladakh-autonomy-draws-thousands-supporters-2024-03-23/</link><description>著名印度活动家索南·旺楚克 (Sonam Wangchuk) 为喜马拉雅山拉达克地区实现自治而进行绝食，他周六表示，禁食已持续到第 18 天，他感到很虚弱，但尽管支持者恳求停止，他仍将按计划继续绝食三天。 。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 09:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-activists-hunger-strike-ladakh-autonomy-draws-thousands-supporters-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>NHK称日本首相承诺增强国防和外交能力以维护和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-pledges-boost-defence-diplomatic-capabilities-preserve-peace-nhk-says-2024-03-23/</link><description>据公共广播公司 NHK 报道，日本首相岸田文雄周六表示，日本将努力加强国防和外交能力以维护和平，并补充说日本各地的军事建设一直在加强。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 07:38:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-pledges-boost-defence-diplomatic-capabilities-preserve-peace-nhk-says-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度在大选前无限期延长洋葱出口禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-extends-ban-onion-exports-indefinitely-ahead-general-election-2024-03-23/</link><description>印度无限期延长对洋葱出口的禁令——这是大选前夕的一个令人惊讶的举动，并将加剧一些海外市场的高价格。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 06:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-extends-ban-onion-exports-indefinitely-ahead-general-election-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警在南海对菲律宾船只使用水炮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-it-took-measures-against-philippine-vessels-south-china-2024-03-23/</link><description>中国海警表示，周六已在南海争议海域对菲律宾船只采取了措施，而菲律宾则谴责这些举措，包括使用高压水枪，称其为“不负责任和挑衅性的”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 02:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-it-took-measures-against-philippine-vessels-south-china-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>天齐锂业在智利SQM-Codelco锂矿交易中寻求股东投票权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tianqi-seeks-shareholder-voting-power-chiles-sqm-codelco-lithium-deal-2024-03-23/</link><description>中国天齐锂业周五敦促智利SQM就与国营铜矿商Codelco讨论的锂交易举行股东投票，并批评谈判缺乏明确性。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 01:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tianqi-seeks-shareholder-voting-power-chiles-sqm-codelco-lithium-deal-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁授予中国金照价值4.05亿美元的港口建设合同</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/peru-awards-chinas-jinzhao-405-million-port-construction-contract-2024-03-22/</link><description>秘鲁政府周五表示，已授予中国金照公司子公司一份在安第斯国家南部建设港口的合同，预计需要 4.05 亿美元的投资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 23:34:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/peru-awards-chinas-jinzhao-405-million-port-construction-contract-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜和中国承诺在北京高层会谈中加强关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-china-held-talks-beijing-kcna-says-2024-03-22/</link><description>朝鲜媒体周日称，朝鲜和中国官员在北京会面，承诺进一步发展双边关系，平壤在因新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 封锁而寻求扩大外交接触。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 21:35:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-china-held-talks-beijing-kcna-says-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>洪都拉斯与中国签署2.75亿美元合作协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/honduras-china-set-275-mln-cooperation-agreement-2024-03-22/</link><description>洪都拉斯政府周五在社交媒体上表示，洪都拉斯和中国签署了一项价值 68 亿伦皮拉（2.7599 亿美元）的合作协议，以帮助加强这个中美洲国家的教育机构基础设施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 19:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/honduras-china-set-275-mln-cooperation-agreement-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>新香港国安法在对自由的担忧中生效</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-hong-kong-national-security-law-comes-into-force-amid-international-2024-03-22/</link><description>尽管国际社会越来越多地批评新的国家安全法可能会侵蚀这座中国统治城市的自由并损害其国际金融中心的信誉，但新的国家安全法于周六在香港生效。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 16:12:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-hong-kong-national-security-law-comes-into-force-amid-international-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰首相因对 ASML 工具许可证存疑而会见中国习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/dutch-pm-meet-chinas-xi-chip-export-policy-strains-ties-2024-03-22/</link><description>知情人士告诉路透社，荷兰首相马克·吕特和中国国家主席习近平将于下周讨论 ASML 是否可以继续为其向中国客户出售的价值数十亿欧元的计算机芯片设备提供服务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 15:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/dutch-pm-meet-chinas-xi-chip-export-policy-strains-ties-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯和中国否决了美国主导的联合国加沙停火决议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-security-council-fails-pass-us-resolution-calling-immediate-ceasefire-gaza-2024-03-22/</link><description>在俄罗斯和中国否决了美国提议的措施后，联合国安理会周五拒绝了一项要求加沙立即停火以及以色列与哈马斯达成人质协议的决议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 13:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-security-council-fails-pass-us-resolution-calling-immediate-ceasefire-gaza-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>全球股票基金因中国数据和美联储降息希望而迎来大量资金流入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-flows-graphic-2024-03-22/</link><description>在中国强劲的工业和零售数据以及对美联储今年晚些时候降息预期的乐观情绪的推动下，截至 3 月 20 日当周，全球股票基金吸引了大量资金流入。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:41:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-flows-graphic-2024-03-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>